<HTML>  <HEAD><TITLE>Sustainable Minnesota Electronic Activist</TITLE></HEAD>  <BODY BACKGROUND="chalk.jpg"> <H1 ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Font Tag --><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Sustainable  Minnesota's<BR>  Electronic Activist Registration</FONT> </H1> Minnesotans for an Energy-Efficient Economy (ME3) is committed to the protection of the economic and environmental health of Minnesota by promoting sustainable  energy policies.  One of our goals is to involve a network of electronic  activists that can be called on from time to time to respond to urgent issues.   You will be alerted to a particular situation and offered some options to enable you to participate in the decisionmaking process.<P>   Fill in the form below, click the Submit button and you will become a registered Electronic Energy Activist and will receive action alerts and news via e-mail as part of our statewide campaign for "smart" energy policies.<P> <HR>  <!-- Form Tag --><FORM ACTION="http://www.mtn.org/cgi-bin/me3-form.cgi"  METHOD="POST">  <B>First Name</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="fname" SIZE=20 ><BR>  <B>Last Name</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="lname" SIZE=20 ><BR>  <B>Organization/Company</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="org"  SIZE=40 ><BR><B>Street Address</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="street1" SIZE=40 ><BR><B>Street Address</B> (line 2)<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="street2" SIZE=35  ><BR> <B>City</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="city" SIZE=20 > <B>State</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="state" SIZE=4 > <B>Zip Code</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="zip" SIZE=10 ><P><B>E-mail Address</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="email" SIZE=35 ><BR><B>Web Page Address</B> (if you have one)<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="url"  SIZE=35 VALUE="http://" ><BR><B>Telephone Number</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="telephone" SIZE=20 > <B>Fax Number</B><INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="fax" SIZE=20 ><P><CENTER><!-- Font Tag --><B><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR="#FF0000">Minnesota Voters Please Fill In The Box Below</FONT></B><P>   <B>Legislative District (ie: 42A, 32B, etc) </B><INPUT TYPE="text"  NAME="district" SIZE=7 ><BR> If you don't know what district you live in try the link below.</CENTER> <CENTER><!-- Table Tag --><TABLE CELLSPACING=1 CELLPADDING=3 BORDER=3><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.pioneerplanet.com/archive/capitol/index.htm">Find Your Legislative District</A> - Using "The Political Machine" </TD></TR> <TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A  HREF="http://www.lmic.state.mn.us/dnet/maps/mnld92.gif">Map of Minnesota  Legislative Districts</A></TD></TR> <TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER><!-- Link Tag --><A  HREF="http://www.lmic.state.mn.us/dnet/answers/bfiles/metld92.gif">Map of Twin  Cities Metropolitan Area Legislative Districts</A></TD></TR>   </TABLE></CENTER><P><B>Please Make Any Additional Comments in this box</B> (optional)<TEXTAREA  NAME="comments" ROWS=10 COLS=50></TEXTAREA><P>   <INPUT TYPE="submit" VALUE="Submit" > <INPUT TYPE="reset" ></FORM> <HR> Return to the <a href="http://www.me3.org">Sustainable Minnesota Home Page</a>  </BODY>  </HTML>
