<H2>News Item - November 13, 1996</H2>

<H2>NSP Seeks Hold On Alternative Storage Site Application<BR></H2>

Northern States Power Company has asked the Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC) to
suspend review of the company's application for a license to construct and operate an alternative
spent nuclear fuel storage facility in Florence Township.<P>

