<HEAD><TITLE>News Item - November 7, 1996-Public Hearings On Electric Industry Restructuring-November 12-December 12 </TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"> 
<H2>News Item - November 7, 1996</H2>
<P>
<H3>ACTION ALERT !</H3>
<H2>Public Hearings On Electric Industry Restructuring<BR></H2>
<!-- Font Tag --><B><FONT SIZE=4 COLOR="#FF0000">Should The Minnesota Public Utilities Commission (PUC) Adopt Changes To The Regulatory Structure of Minnesota's Electric Utilities?</FONT></B><P>

<HR>
Following is a list of dates and times that have been scheduled around Minnesota for public hearings regarding the proposed deregulation of the electric power industry in Minnesota.  These hearings will provide the PUC with an opportunity to learn what the public's concerns and priorities are with respect to utility deregulation.<P>



For more information contact the PUC at 612-296-8667.  By the way, as long as you are calling, let them know they should get a website!<P>

<HR>
<UL>
<LI><B>November 12, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Bemidji, MN</B><BR>
Bemidji State University, "Crying Wolf Room", Beaux Arts Hobson Memorial Union<P>



<LI><B>November 13, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Hinckley, MN</B><BR>
Hinckley City Hall, 106 First Street SE<P>

<LI><B>November 19, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Duluth, MN</B><BR>
Duluth City Hall, 4th Avenue West & 1st Street<P>

<LI><B>November 21, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Rochester, MN</B><BR>
Rochester City Hall, 1st Avenue & 3rd Street SW<P>

<LI><B>November 26, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Marshall, MN</B><BR>
Marshall City Hall, 344 West Main Street<P>

<LI><B>December 3, 1996-Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Plymouth, MN</B><BR>
Plymouth Administrative Offices, 3400 Plymouth Blvd.<P>

<LI><B>December 4, 1996-Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Stillwater, MN</B><BR>
Washington County Courthouse, 14900 North 61st Street<P>

<LI><B>December 5, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Alexandria, MN</B><BR>
Douglas County Public Works Center, 509 3rd Avenue West<P>

<LI><B>December 10, 1996-Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Minneapolis, MN</B><BR>
Hennepin County Government Center, 300 South 6th Street<P>

<LI><B>December 12, 1996-Afternoon 1:30 pm and Evening 6:30 pm</B><BR>
<B>Roseville, MN</B><BR>
Roseville Activity Center, 2800 Arona Street (1 block E & 1 block S. of County Road C2 and Snelling Avenue)<P>

