<P> <!-- Link Tag -->
<LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.revisor.leg.state.mn.us:70/00/.revisor/senate/publicbills/1995-1996/S2700-2799/S2721">Full Text of EEPRA Bill SF (2721)</A><P><P>
</UL>



