<!-- Link Tag -->
<LI><LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.revisor.leg.state.mn.us:70/00/.revisor/senate/bill_tracking/number/1995-1996/SF2000-2099/SF2040">Status of the SF 2040</A><P>

<LI> <A HREF="amocobill.html">Testimony Before the Senate Jobs, Energy and Community Development Committee</A> by David Morris, vice president of the Institute for Local Self-Reliance.  February 13, 1996
