	<H3>7670.1115 EFFECTIVE DATES</H3>


	The effective date of amendments to this chapter is June 16, 1994.<P>



	EXCEPTION:  Effective January 1, 1998, residential buildings (one-and two-family and other residential buildings three stories or less in height) must meet the requirements of the R-2000 Home Program Technical Requirements, Canadian Home Builders' Association, September 1992.<P>



