<HEAD><TITLE>MAJOR FEDERAL ENVIRONMENTAL LAWS</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY> 
<H2>MAJOR FEDERAL ENVIRONMENTAL LAWS</H2>

These laws, enacted since Earth Day 1970, are referenced here because several of Minnesota's environmental laws stem from federal directives.<P>

