<H3>November 19, 1996</H3>
Added the following to <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.me3.org/issues/merger/">Utility Merger Information Page</A>: <!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=2>(Can you tell the Primergy merger issue is heating up?)</FONT><P>
<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.me3.org/issues/merger/staymotion.html">Motion For Stay Of Proceeding And Request For Certification To The Commission  Of Petition Of The Environmental Coalition, Energy Cents Coalition And Citizens' Utility Board For Reconsideration And Rehearing Of Order Finding No Prohibited Ex Parte Communication</A> - Before the Minnesota Office of Administrative Hearings, November 18, 1996
