<H3>November 18, 1996</H3>
A coalition of organizations including ME3, Izaak Walton League and the Environmental Law & Policy Center of the Midwest have intervened in the Wisconsin, Minnesota, and Federal regulatory proceedings pertaining to the NSP/WEC proposal to form the mega-utility, Primergy.  Here are some of the filings added to the <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.me3.org/issues/merger/">Utility Merger Information Page</A>:<P>
<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.me3.org/issues/merger/brick.html">Direct Testimony of Stephen Brick</A> - Before the Minnesota PUC, November 1996<BR>
<!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.me3.org/issues/merger/mendl.html">Direct Testimony of Jerry Mendl</A> - Before the Minnesota PUC, November 1996<P> 

