<TITLE>
Electric Utility Merger Issue Page
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">
<CENTER><H1>Electric Utility Merger Information</H1></CENTER>
<HR>
<H2>NSP/WEC Primergy Merger Information</H2>

<H3>Environmental Coalition Regulatory Intervention Materials</H3>
A coalition of organizations including ME3, Izaak Walton League and the Environmental Law & Policy Center have intervened in the Wisconsin, Minnesota, and Federal regulatory proceedings pertaining to the Northern States Power Company (NSP) and Wisconsin Energy Corporation (WEC) proposal to form the mega-utility, Primergy.  Here are some of the filings outlining the coalition positions on various aspects of the merger proposal.
