<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.tellus.com/">Tellus Institute</A>  
<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.ucsusa.org/">Union of Concerned Scientists</A>
<LI> <!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.usgcrp.gov/">U.S. Global Change Research Program (USGCRP)</A>
