<H3>Other Web Pages Covering Environmental Externalities</H3>

<B>Mercury</B><P>
ME3 has been supporting the efforts to quantify the environmental effects of mercury pollution.  The United States Environmental Protection Agency is trying to avoid releasing a significant study on the effects of mercury on human health and the environment to the US Congress.  MSB Energy Associates has provided ME3 with the materials below and are urging you to contact your Congressional representative to ensure that the findings of this massive study are released.<P>

For more information please contact:
<!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=2><CENTER>David Oppenheimer<BR>
MSB Energy Associates, Inc.<BR>
7507 Hubbard Ave., Suite 200<BR>
Middleton, WI  53562-3135 <BR>
phone: (608) 831-1127  extension 309 <BR>
fax: (608) 836-1290 <BR> 
E-mail: <!-- MailTo Tag --><A HREF="MAILTO:opp@msbnrg.com">opp@msbnrg.com</A> </CENTER></FONT>
