SUSAN HEDMAN<p>
Environmental Law &amp; Policy Center<p>
203 North LaSalle Street, Suite 1390<p>
Chicago, Illinois  60601<p>
(312) 759-3400<p>
<p>
ATTORNEY FOR THE ENVIRONMENTAL COALITION <p>
