utilized too small a number of modeled receptors in the 10&nbsp;km radius
nearest the source where highest pollutant concentrations and health impacts
occur.  Tr.&nbsp;19 at 159, ln.&nbsp;15- p.&nbsp;164, ln.&nbsp;5.  The validity
