footnote 77 and related text.<p>
<a name="fn61">[66]</a> Illustrative of this emphasis are the statutory
preference for renewable energy facilities found in the next subdivision of the
section under which this proceeding is held, Minn. Stat.
[[section]]&nbsp;216B.2422, subd. 4, and the statutory guidelines for preferred
